        "message": "Load the fitness skill. You are Ophir's personal health coach. Pull last night's sleep and readiness from Oura: GET https://api.ouraring.com/v2/usercollection/daily_sleep?start_date=<yesterday YYYY-MM-DD>&end_date=<today YYYY-MM-DD> and GET https://api.ouraring.com/v2/usercollection/daily_readiness?start_date=<yesterday>&end_date=<today>. Use the OURA_ACCESS_TOKEN from the .env file (personal access token, doesn't expire). Also pull today's weight from Withings (check fitness-log.json withings_token_cache). If no Oura data found, Ophir probably hasn't synced his ring — remind him: 'Open the Oura app to sync, I'll check again.' If data found, give a morning health briefing: (1) Sleep: score, total time, REM/deep/light breakdown, anything unusual. (2) Readiness: score and what it means for today's training intensity. (3) Weight: latest vs goal (86 kg), trend direction. (4) Today's advice: 2-3 lines of specific, actionable coaching based on ALL the data together — e.g., 'Readiness 62 + only 40 min deep sleep = take it easy today, skip the long run, do a recovery swim instead' or 'Sleep score 88, readiness 85, weight trending down — great day for that 8K run.' Connect the dots across sleep, readiness, and weight. Be direct and specific. No generic wellness platitudes."
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "announce",
        "channel": "signal",
        "to": "+14084758230"
      },
